s:742:"<p>The settings panel for specific rows or groups of modules are shown when the user clicks on the edit pencil for that specific row.</p>
<p><strong>The Row settings panel allows the user to control specific responsive settings, colours, margins, paddings etc for that specific row.</strong></p>
<h2>How to activate the Row settings</h2>
<ol>
<li>Click on the pencil in a row.</li>
</ol>
<p><img style="" alt="Logo pencil click" src="/docs/buildr-documentation/user/pages/06.row-settings/logo-edit.png" /></p>
<ol>
<li>Once the user has clicked on the icon the settings available for that row will appear</li>
</ol>
<p><img style="" alt="Logo Row Settings" src="/docs/buildr-documentation/user/pages/06.row-settings/logo-row-style.png" /></p>";